RELEASE 1.1 (unreleased)
CHANGES SINCE 1.0:
================================================================================
MAJOR CHANGES:
 * buildMessageFromArray (in the abstract writer) will no longer return html
   tables, but instead a print_r like formatted message.
 * new buildHtmlMessageFromArray function who's basically the old
   buildMessageFromArray function
MINOR CHANGES:
 * Added more examples
BUG FIXES:
 * Fixed a mispelled constant in the syslog writer
 * Fixed bugged format replacer